<item>
            <title>[ELY-784] Schema problems in elytron-1_0.xsd</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/ELY-784</link>
                <project id="12315320" key="ELY">WildFly Elytron</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like I made a mistake in the XSD - for whatever reason I was under the impression that it was possible to embed a &quot;choice&quot; under an &quot;all&quot;; my IDE now has decided to point out that this is not allowed (not sure why it didn&apos;t do so earlier).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So now there needs to be a solution which allows this element setup, hopefully without resorting to &quot;sequence&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
